{"tid":1576190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港共逃避工程責任？】港鐵凌晨維修路軌，4個鐘後出軌","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:11:31.000Z","uid":98842,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c174960828c5e53af80c36f29a3cf98eb6ea6c1","tid":1576190,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLKfiDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLKfiDv.jpg&h=710d722d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工程時間：0100-0455<br />\n<br />\n港共作為擁有75.28%黨鐵股份大股東，<br />\n黨鐵一切意外自然責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n意外於工程維修後4小時，<br />\n馬上發生香港史無前例的載人的列車出軌，<br />\n到底是否工程維修導致是次事故，<br />\n還是根本一直偷工減料導致？<br />\n<br />\n建議在列車受傷乘客必需將責任追究到底，<br />\n不論身體受傷，及日後對地鐵產生恐懼。"},{"pid":"aabb2e099c96fb9c8d3861e01798abfc368b71db","tid":1576190,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"cb66bed07e1790a11ad4abf8eadd4577711f5c03","tid":1576190,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59cd0b8ff647c8a878dafb43bc0ee53627a17cb8","tid":1576190,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"Fact Check模式統一化提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1576054/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1576054/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a4dca03b78b8ad13